KCC First Introduction: MomDoge is a fully Decentralized Exchange that runs on Binance Smart Chain, Bridging your assets across networks is faster and cheaper using MomDogeSwap.
KCC Second Introduction: Its purpose is to solve the problems such as low performance and high cost of public chain, to provide community users with faster, more convenient and low-cost experience.
KCC INTRODUCE 1: Swapping is faster than ever and cross-chain bridging is an unique solution for transfering all your assets across networks like Binance smart chain.
KCC INTRODUCE 2: MomDoge token will be a deflationary token with a unique burn mechanism. You will be able to farm MomDoge using different liquidity pairs. AMM by itself will provide high yield farms for early investors and for the long term HODL community.
KCC INTRODUCE 3: You can stake stable coins like BNB, BUSD, USDT or MomDoge token and earn MomDoge tokens as rewards. By adding your liquidity pairs to the farm you will be able to earn MomDoge tokens as rewards.
KCC INTRODUCE 4: Increasing number of BSC yield farms has become difficult to watch your farms in different places. We have come up with a solution where you can watch all your farms in one location.
